Project Name:FilmFInder
Author: Boniface Cheruiyot

Description
The FilmFinder movie Search Application is a web-based tool that allows users to search for movies using the OMDB API. Users can enter a movie title in the search box, and the application will provide a list of matching movies. Selecting a movie from the list displays detailed information about the chosen film, including its title, year of release, ratings, plot, and more

Project Setup Instructions
Follow these steps to set up and run the Movie Search Application locally on your machine

Clone the Repository:
sh
in your terminal
git clone https://github.com/kieyp/Project-FilmFinder.git

Navigate to the project directory
in your terminal
cd filfinder

https://github.com/kieyp/Project-FilmFinder.git

Open index.html in Your Browser:

Double-click index.html or right-click and choose "Open with" to launch the application in your default web browser.

